llWwC8jZwjw.title: Christmas Cardio Workout! Fun fat burning workout to your favorite holiday songs!!
llWwC8jZwjw.description:
You guys, isn't the holiday season the best time of the year? There are so many fun things about the holidays...the songs, the decorations, the movies, the presents, the cookies and ALL THE FOOD.
I put together this awesome cardio routine for you using my most favorite Christmas songs to help us all get in the Christmas spirit! You're going to be doing squats, you're going to be doing lunges, you're going be doing butt-ups...but you won't even notice you're working out because you will be having so much fun. So grab a friend or family member and let's get started!!

Song list:
Jingle Bell Rock - Glee Cast 00:38
Holly Jolly Christmas - Michael Buble 3:12
Arian Grande - Last Christmas 5:15

Hundreds - to warm up your core and prep you for the rest of the workout
Ab challenge - to get your abdominal muscles tight and toned
Butt challenge - to lift and round your flutes
Crazy cardio - to get your heart rate up and burn fat

lQDrPsPodA0.title: 10 Minute Anti-Bloating Cardio (Low impact)
lQDrPsPodA0.description:
Bloat. We've all been there. Wanna know the secret to reducing bloat? The best way to get rid of all that uncomfortable gas is to drink lots of water and get your body moving!

Today, we're gonna do a 10 minute cardio routine that has NO jumping, so it will be super easy on the stomach! We'll do each move for 45 seconds with a 15 second rest in between. Ready? Let's go.

00:00 Intro
00:53 Squatting Floor Touches
1:54 Plank Walk Openers
2:52 Side Squats
3:50 Curtsey Lunge Kick - R
4:49 Curtsey Lunge Kick - L
5:50 Squat to Kick
6:50 Prisoner Stairs
7:52 Lunge Around the World
8:50 Inchworms
9:58 Dancing Dog
10:48 Stretch
11:45 Outro

#bloat #cardio #workout #cardioworkout #blogilates

w0h5CpZZRvM.title: GOOD BOOTY DEATH - Cassey Ho ft. Schmoyoho (official music video)
w0h5CpZZRvM.description:
So this is TOTALLY random but here's a music video I made with The Gregory Brothers from @schmoyoho! I've been a HUGE FAN of their quirky songs since "Bed Intruder" and "Dead Giveaway". OMG just thinking of "Dead Giveaway" makes me laugh.

Anyway, I met The Gregory Brothers at the YouTube Creator Summit last year and I was like ummmmm would you be interested in collaborating!!??? I was so happy when they said yes! That is how this random music video came to be. They took one of my weird lines "Good booty death" and made a whole song out of it. OMG IT IS SO WEIRD BUT I LOVE IT.

I hope you like the song!! Should I make a butt workout video to "Good Booty Death"??

Download the song here:
Apple music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/good-booty-death-single/1540754930?ls=1
iTunes: https://music.apple.com/us/album/good-booty-death-single/1540754930?ls=1&app=itunes
Spotify URL: http://open.spotify.com/album/0FvSyU35AIJihl8ySC7L8g
Spotify URI: spotify:album:0FvSyU35AIJihl8ySC7L8g
Subscribe to Schmoyoho: https://www.youtube.com/c/songify

Chorus
I am shaking
My butt is vibrating
Boom my gosh, do you feel
Hooo whoooo the burn is real
The hamstrings are the elevator to the butt
So I am not giving up, I am not giving up
I am dying, really dying
Find your strength go even higher
Look inside for your confidence
Make them sexy straighten out that leg
Die with me, gonna be a good booty death
Good booty death x3
Gonna be a good booty death
Verse
Your body is going to be feeling it, but your spirit will also be lifted
We’re nearing the end of the race, keep following the light to the ribbon
Go even higher this time, find your strength
Look inside for your confidence, don’t shove it away
You could be doing this naked and I wouldn’t even know
But PUT DOWN that can of coke!
Confidence has to come from looking inside
Then you’ll love what you see in the mirror next time
Chorus
If you’re holding a bag of chips, shove it away
Focus on having fun, getting through butt day
Shove it away, shove it away
Focus on having fun, getting through butt day
Make sure you are working hard
Are you having fun? 
I know you are!
Chorus

R_Plqh8j_Kg.title: Ariel's Abs - Disney Princess Ab Workout
R_Plqh8j_Kg.description:
Today we are doing Ariel's abs workout!! In my Belle's Beast Mode Bootcamp video, I asked you guys which Disney princess you'd want to work out with next and I'm soooooo happy most of you said Ariel!!!! I had lots of fun coming up with the exercise names & picking out the perfect Ariel costume.

Today, we're doing Ariel's quick ab workout with 7 moves, 45 seconds on, 15 seconds off. Are you ready to go under the sea?!?!

00:00 Intro
2:28 Prince Eric's Earthquake

r4u2MNHC-3U.title: Why I stepped on the scale again...
r4u2MNHC-3U.description:
Trigger warning. I am talking about scales today. Yup. And I know how most people feel about scales. We hate them, stepping on them gives us anxiety, and throwing them away feels like freedom. But I am here to tell you that throwing away the scale isn't always the solution. Maybe for some of us, but not all of us. The scale can still be useful IF you are able to remove the emotional and self worthiness component awat from the number. Speaking from my own personal experience here, I have gone through soooooo many different stages of relationships with the scale and I am going to show you how I went from being afraid of the scale to hating the scale to throwing away to scale to having a major BREAKTHROUGH with the scale. I am going to show you how I freed myself from the scale’s power, and put that power back in MY hands and how you can do the exact same thing!

yLcvuN5Yru8.title: When you're not good enough...
yLcvuN5Yru8.description:
You guys, there is something I need to get off of my chest...I am SICK of having my body define who I am. Those of you who have been with me the last ten years know that I have not always been a "skinny" fitness instructor. When I first started teaching online, I was the "inspiring" and "body positive" "fat" instructor. Now that I have achieved my own personal fitness goal, you know, practiced what I preached, I have somehow turned into a "fat shaming" and "irresponsible" "skinny" instructor...How does that even make sense?! I am literally the exact same person teaching the exact same things! I mean, my number one goal over the years has always been to help YOU reach YOUR goals. What kind of an example would I be setting if I didn't reach my own goals?? This culture of body shaming has to stop. We are all people just trying our best to feel good about ourselves. No matter my size, I am just the same Cassey who only wants the best for you.

Qe5b3LErOBQ.title: Weight loss: guys vs girls - it's so unfair!
Qe5b3LErOBQ.description:
I definitely know from experience how hard it can be putting in sooo much time and effort into exercising to lose weight and build muscle, only to come out with little to no results. And when I see the guys around me doing the same thing I am, and getting results so much faster than I am, while eating whatever they want - I just feel I am doing something wrong! I know I'm not, but it feel so unfair!

It turns out that there is actually science behind WHY this is the case! If you stick with me, I promise that by the end of this video, you will have a new found respect and love for your own beautiful body and a perspective shift that will help carry you through the hard times on your own fitness journey. 

Today's featured letter:

Dear Cassey, I have taken to committing to my health both mentally and physically. I definitely feel guilty about one cheat meal or snack even though 90% of my diet is healthy. The problem is my partner can eat whatever he wants and he never seems to have a problem with weight. He puts on 5 pounds he loses 12, it’s so frustrating when I am fighting tooth and nail for the 1lb mark. And his diet won’t be as healthy as mine, and his mindset is, I can eat what I want when I want and burn it off later. What can I do so that I don’t resent him, and also so that I’m not so hard on myself?

Sincerely,
Resentful

Dear Cassey,

I'm hoping for some advice or maybe just some feedback to help me with understanding my current situation and motivation. I'm overweight, and I always have been. Sincerely,
Unhappy and Unmotivated

cyx0lb-a_bs.title: 10 Minute Beautiful Thigh Sculpt Pilates Workout | 7 Day Thigh Challenge (Days 4-7)
cyx0lb-a_bs.description:
Join me for the #7DayThighChallenge!!! https://www.blogilates.com/7-day-thigh-challenge-2020/

These are your LAST five moves of the 7 Day Thigh Challenge and I want you to give them 110%!!!! Think about how strong and accomplished you're gonna feel at the end. So proud of you all for making it this far!!

7 DAY THIGH CHALLENGE:

Purpose: To slim and sculpt your thighs in 7 days!
Begins: Monday May 25, 2020
Ends: Sunday June 1, 2020
Length: 7 days
Daily commitment: 20-30 min

How it works:
Day 1-7: Take a before picture of your legs & complete the workouts listed for the day. You can even film yourself doing these and have a cool progress video that you can upload to Instagram, TikTok, or YouTube at the end of the week!
Day 1-7: Make sure to drink at least 64 oz of water a day for all 7 days.
Day 1-7: Make sure to reduce your intake of refined/processed carbs (bread, crackers, cereal, pastries etc.) and replace with whole vegetables and fruits for 7 days.
End of Day 7: Take an after picture or video of your legs and upload the results to Instagram, TikTok, or YouTube! Make sure to include the #7DayThighChallenge hashtag and tag @blogilates so other users can find the challenge!

Day 1-7: Make sure to reduce your intake of refined/processed carbs (bread, crackers, cereal, pastries etc.) and replace with whole vegetables and fruits for 7 days.
End of Day 7: Take an after picture or video of your abs and upload the results to Instagram, TikTok, or YouTube! Make sure to include the #7DayAbChallenge hashtag and tag @blogilates so other users can find the challenge!

1. Jump squats
2. Hip twists
3. Plank jacks
4. Double leg lifts
5. Plank jack pikes
6. Star abs
7. Flutters

cO7iMCci904.title: Extreme Abs Workout | 25 Min At Home Upper Abs, Lower Abs, Obliques & Total Core Pilates Routine
cO7iMCci904.description:
You guys!! I can't believe we hit 5 million!!! 10 years ago, I was uploading YouTube videos to just 40 of my students. NOW THERE'S 5 MILLION OF YOU?! From the bottom of my heart, thank you all for continuing to work out with me. Hope we can keep having fun together!

To celebrate, I put together the HARDEST, most insane ab workout EVER! It's a 5x5 workout, which means we're gonna do 5 rounds with 5 different moves in each round, each focusing on different abdominal muscles. That’s 25 different ab exercises in 25 minutes!

Round 1: UPPER ABS

1. HUNDREDS
2. TABLETOP CRUNCH
3. TOE TOUCHES
4. CRESCENT CRUNCH
5. BUTTERFLY CRUNCH

Round 2: LOWER ABS

1. DOUBLE LEG LIFTS
2. SINGLE LEG DROP
3. REVERSE CRUNCHES
4. FLUTTERS
5. DOUBLE D’S

Round 3: CENTER ABS

1. SINGLE STRAIGHT LEG STRETCH
2. DOUBLE LEG STRETCH
3. STAR ABS
4. EAGLE CRUNCH
5. SINGLE LEGGED JACKKNIFE

Round 4: OBLIQUES

1. CANDLESTICK DIPPER R
2. SIDE PLANK DIPPERS R
3. CANDLESTICK DIPPERS L
4. SIDE PLANK DIPPERS L
5. HIP TWIST BUTT UPS

Round 5: TOTAL CORE

1. ROLLOVERS
2. ROLL UP
3. SPRINTER
4. EARTHQUAKE
5. PLANK

Love you guys!! 

P.S. I'm wearing my brand new POPFLEX set from the Terrain Collection!! Get yours at https://www.popflexactive.com/!

V1Yc8JZlHKM.title: Toned Arms at Home Workout! Apartment Friendly ☺️
V1Yc8JZlHKM.description:
I asked you guys what workouts you wanna do at home and a lot of you asked for weights. And because not everyone has dumbbells, I decided to get creative.

Why not wine bottles (or water bottles or soup cans etc)?! I tested this on TikTok and you guys LOVED it, so here it is: my first full length wine bottle arm workout!

Your biceps, triceps & shoulders are gonna be SHAKING once you're done with this! You've got 10 moves, one minute on, 10 seconds off (don't worry, there's a timer).

1. Bicep Curls
2. Tricep Pulse
3. Prayer Pulse
4. Shoulder Press
5. Double Tray Opens
6. Front Raises
7. Reverse Flys
8. Press & Close
9. L Raises
10. Upright Row

Workout starts at 1:41!

_8vGQR0zxDM.title: 10 Minute Waist Whittler | Total Body Transformation Workout
_8vGQR0zxDM.description:
Congrats!!!! You made it to the end of the Total Body Transformation series!! You guys this workout series was NOT easy, so you should be proud of yourself for making it here!

Today we're hyper-targeting the waist, especially those obliques to create that natural corset around your waist. If you've been looking for a workout that will give you a natural hourglass shape, this is it you guys!!

You have 8 oblique moves today. We'll do each for 1 minute with a 15 second break in between. They are:

1. Standing Side Crunch (R)
2. Standing Side Crunch (L)
3. Reaching Candlestick (R)
4. X Candlestick (R)
5. Elbow Tap Side Plank (R)
6. Reaching Candlestick (L)
7. X Candlestick (L)
8. Elbow Tap Side Plank (L)

Workout starts at 2:22!

_AsSCHTnb0g.title: Don't like your body? This video will change that.
_AsSCHTnb0g.description:
Join my 7-Day Body Love Challenge! Get the graphic here: https://www.instagram.com/p/B8MwU3Fn6ph/

Loving your body begins with loving you as a whole. Your body is not a separate thing from your mind, your heart, or your soul. Every part of you is interconnected, and a change in one will change the other parts of you too. That’s why when you go on a quest to transform your body, you’re actually on a journey to transform your mind as well.

Alright you guys, I’m gonna leave you with this: Today I want you to let go of your insecurities and embrace yourself fully, as one complete and beautiful human being. Don’t ever forget that. You are a complete and beautiful human being.

x_l04xDK9-E.description:

3. Their goals are too focused on the results and not the journey.

kEiPal3RrKw.title: The Unusual Beauty Standard for Fitness Girls...
kEiPal3RrKw.description:
Instagram is like high school...except there's concrete evidence who's the most popular, aka how many followers you have. And guess what happens when you're popular? Everyone wants to be like you, talk like you, dress like you, look like you and pretty much BE YOU. 

So, I wanted to decode the Instagram beauty standard for fitness influencers. What aesthetics make you one of the most followed women in the female fitness category? Age
Height
Eye color
Eye size

Hair length
Definition on their stomach
Lip size
Skin color
Ethnicity
Face shape
Prominence of butt
Nose size
Overall body shape

I think you will be shocked to see the results.

BT-r3w1m5U0.title: Women try guessing each other’s weight | A social experiment
BT-r3w1m5U0.description:
This video isn't like anything I have EVER done before, and it all started with a few questions I had. 

Why do we allow our weight to control our feelings?
Why do we give the scale so much power?
What does BMI really mean?
Is body fat percentage actually a better indicator of health?

I decided to gather a bunch of women together to run a “little” social experiment to find out how all of these things - BMI, weight, body fat percentage - actually looked like on a woman. And I wanted to see if we could tell which was most accurate. Or would we find out that labels are bogus?

I started planning this video a year ago, and I had NO IDEA how to pull it off. Fast forward to shoot day and we had a 20+ person crew working on it AND we flew out one of the world's best female bodybuilders...from Sweden!!!! So crazy!!!!!!

Parts of this video were extremely uncomfortable to film, but I hope you guys take away the fact that there is so much more to a person than their number.

I have so many people to thank for making this video happen - my amazing director Ryan, my husband Sam, the crew, the Blogifam...but most of all I want to thank all of the brave, strong women for speaking their truths. You all are amazing!

Ncuh7cfF2RI.title: The Complicated World of Body Positivity (a mini documentary)
Ncuh7cfF2RI.description:
Body positivity. It’s not as straightforward as you think. I used to think I was being body positive if I loved my body, but apparently, it’s not that simple.

After embarking on my 90 day journey, I got so much negativity and backlash from fans saying that I hated my body. Did having a weight loss goal make me automatically a bad role for body positivity? Did having a fat loss goal make me automatically anti body positive?

I wanted to know if I had ever misused the term “body positivity.” I wanted to know what it really meant, where the movement came from, and who body positivity was actually made for. Are thin people allowed to be a part of the body positive movement or is it just for fat people? I wanted to know if I was out of line.

So, I did some heavy research and conducted interviews with women who were actively involved in the body positive community.

Big thank you to the following women!

Connie Sobczak
Website: https://www.thebodypositive.org/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/conniesobczak

Simone Mariposa
Blog: https://simonemariposa.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/simonemariposa

Lexi Eleni Placourakis:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lexieleni

Natasha Rusilko
Website: https://www.nourished-natasha.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nourishednatasha

Writer & Executive Producer: Cassey Ho
Cinematographer, Sound & Producer: Sam Livits
Editor: Danielle Murray

New York Times: https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/29/opinion/weight-loss-body-positivity.html

After embarking on my 90 day journey, I got so much negativity and backlash from fans saying that I hated my body. Did having a weight loss goal make me automatically a bad role for body positivity? Did having a fat loss goal make me automatically anti body positive?

I wanted to know if I had ever misused the term “body positivity.” I wanted to know what it really meant, where the movement came from, and who body positivity was actually made for. Are thin people allowed to be a part of the body positive movement or is it just for fat people? I wanted to know if I was out of line.

So, I did some heavy research and conducted interviews with women who were actively involved in the body positive community.

Big thank you to the following women!

Connie Sobczak
Website: https://www.thebodypositive.org/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/conniesobczak

Simone Mariposa
Blog: https://simonemariposa.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/simonemariposa

Lexi Eleni Placourakis:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lexieleni

Natasha Rusilko
Website: https://www.nourished-natasha.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nourishednatasha

Writer & Executive Producer: Cassey Ho
Cinematographer, Sound & Producer: Sam Livits
Editor: Danielle Murray

Sources:
New York Times: https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/29/opinion/weight-loss-body-positivity.html

qxGzVxs3D_0.title: Relaxing stretches for better sleep & increased flexibility (you can do in bed!)
qxGzVxs3D_0.description:
We all know that getting exercise and feeding your body right is important when it comes to getting fit and healthy. But a lot of times, we THINK we are doing everything we are supposed to do but actually, we are not. There is one more thing we need to concentrate on - SLEEP.

If you don't sleep enough, you put your body under stress. If you are stressed, you can't get the results you want. Stress makes it hard to gain muscle and lose fat. Stress makes it DIFFICULT to lose weight when your body is not well rested!

SO! Today, I am showing you a full bed time stretching routine that will relax you and get you ready to fall asleep. Do this with me at night and you will have a deeper, more relaxing sleep that will leave you feeling rejuvenated and recharged when you wake up! These stretches will also help you increase flexibility.

C9eK5mSHgCs.title: 10 years ago today.... *EMOTIONAL*
C9eK5mSHgCs.description:
Today is the 10 year anniversary of Blogilates! EEEEEEEE! That's a squeal, btw.

It is so surreal to think, in 2009, I started uploading videos to YouTube for my pilates students that I thought NO ONE would ever see! I can't believe how lucky I am to be able to be a fitness trainer & friend to over 4.7 million of you now! 

I hope you guys love this look at the past 10 years! It's crazy to see how much has changed (like my hair, haha) and how much has stayed the same (booty taps for life)!

Thank you to everyone who stayed with me on this journey, and I can't wait to do more amazing stuff with you guys!

5HJ8du5i_rE.title: Decoding the Instagram Beauty Standard
5HJ8du5i_rE.description:
Influencers have now become the new beauty standard.
But what exactly is the new beauty standard? Well, I decided to find out for myself. I made a list of the Top 100 female Instagram stars purely based on following. Then I came up with 22 attributes that each woman would be judged on. These included things like:

Hair color
Hair length
Neck length
Face shape
Body shape
Eye color
Clothing size
Flatness of stomach
Lip size
Eye size
Nose size
Skin color
Chest size
Prominence of butt
Age
Height...etc

After a couple weeks of gathering data and categorizing data, I can tell you that there is most definitely a formula and a specific beauty standard that the 100 most followed women on Instagram adhere to. 

Watch the video to find out the results and to see me get photoshopped into a Top 100 Female Instagrammer!

OyaMpFt9fSk.title: I'm taking the 100 Glute Challenge. You in?
OyaMpFt9fSk.description:
#100glutechallenge printable: https://www.blogilates.com/100glutechallenge/

You guys, this is the moment you've all been waiting for!!! A week from today, we're starting a brand new 100 Challenge!! I've been dying to tell you guys. Are you ready to hear what body part we'll be targeting??? It's gonna be...glutes!!! 

The 100 Glute Challenge starts August 4th! I've picked 30 butt workouts that will target ALL parts of your booty! That means we're doing 100 reps of a glute move every day for 30 days! 
Plus, I'll have a new guest joining me EVERY DAY and you may see some familiar faces! Let's make this EVEN BIGGER than the 100 AB Challenge. Remember, Taylor Swift did the 100 Ab Challenge - so I mean BIG, PEOPLE!

I'll also be doing an Instagram giveaway on @popflex_active every week during the challenge! Every Friday, I'm giving away a pair of the peach socks and one of the peach hair ties I am wearing to 5 lucky winners! So that is 20 winners total!

To enter:

1. On Instagram, upload a picture or video of yourself doing the challenge! Be sure to upload to your feed, use the hashtag #100GluteChallenge and tag @blogilates and @popflex_active.

2. Make sure you are following @popflex_active, @blogilates, and @poppilatesofficial.

Each post will count as one entry & the giveaway is open worldwide to POPsters of all ages! LET'S DO THIS!!!

localized.description:

You guys, this is the moment you've all been waiting for!!! A week from today, we're starting a brand new 100 Challenge!! I've been dying to tell you guys. Are you ready to hear what body part we'll be targeting??? It's gonna be...glutes!!!

UuCTUGXieMM.title: BAD GUY BOOTY! A glute workout inspired by Billie Eilish
UuCTUGXieMM.description:
It's a Billie Eilish's "Bad Guy" booty workout! Today we're doing a choreographed glute workout routine to the biggest song of the top pop charts -"Bad Guy". This song was weird, creepy, poppy, and super unusual to choreograph to. I had fun a lot of fun playing with the beats and making a solid butt workout for you.

BAD GUY BOOTY WORKOUT:

(INSTRUMENTAL)

- Plank Jacks x 8

(VERSE 1)

- Cross butt kick right x 8
- Pointed Butt Lift right x 16

(VERSE 2)

- Straight heel lifts right x 8
- Hammy curls right x 4

(CHORUS)

- Plank Jacks x 16

(VERSE 3)

- Cross butt kick left x 8
- Pointed Butt Lift left x 16

(VERSE 4)

- Straight heel lifts left x 8
- Hammy curls left x 4

(CHORUS)

- High heel single legged bridge right x 16
- High heel single legged bridge left x 16

(BRIDGE - END)

- Long bridges x 2, flexed leg raise x 1 (5 times right)
- Long bridges x 2, flexed leg raise x 1 (5 times left)

My top & yoga mat are from: http://www.popflexactive.com

ILmSnFunyJo.title: Fat Burn Machine *FULL LENGTH 30 Minute PIIT28 Workout*
ILmSnFunyJo.description:
Become a certified PIIT28 Trainer! https://www.piit28.com/getcertified The workshop is online, so you can do it right from home!

To celebrate the launch of the PIIT28 Trainer Certification, I’m releasing my first ever FULL LENGTH PIIT28 class!

Today you’ll get to experience Pilates Intense Interval Training the way it will be taught as a class by instructors, live at gyms!

This workout combines the fat burning intensity of HIIT and the muscle toning power of pilates! We will start with a quick dynamic warm up followed by six power-packed moves - 45 seconds on, 15 seconds off. After 4 rounds, we'll do a Core Burnout for your abs!

Today’s class is called FAT BURN MACHINE by PIIT28. It’s a total body cardio and body toning workout.

Your PIIT moves are:

1. Squat Hop
2. Tricep Kick & Dip
3. Push Up Burpees
4. Plank Twist Up
5. Plie Hop
6. Standing Rollover

Now imagine...you can become a PIIT28 certified trainer and teach this class to your own students! You don’t need any pre-requisites. I’ll teach you everything you need to know in the training portal. And when you finish training, you’ll know all the techniques, all the modifications, and how to create your own routines! 

Get certified here: https://www.piit28.com/getcertified

No matter where you live, you can get certified right from home! 

#cardioworkout #pilates #piit28 #blogilates #cardio

T4adtRJ_b3g.description:
Download your 28 Day Summer Sculpt workout calendar: https://www.blogilates.com/28daysummersculpt/

I know a lot of you guys are all about reaching for flatter abs and a rounder booty (I mean, I am too sometimes) but let's forget about these physical goals for a second and just focus on having fun!! If you aim towards having a stronger mindset, the abs and booty will follow!!

Are you ready for today's total warm up, workout & cool down? We're gonna do all ten moves together and then do them again to complete the 24 minute workout!

Your Abs and Butt Exercises:

Criss Cross
Single Legged Jackknives
V-Ups
Dancer’s Sweep right
Dancer’s Pulse right
Dancer’s Kick and Tap right
Dancer’s Sweep left
Dancer’s Pulse left
Dancer’s Kick and Tap left
Double Leg Lift Crunch

ebm3zAoUpGE.title: 3 Minute Tippy Toes Leg Slimming Workout | POP Pilates Song Challenge
ebm3zAoUpGE.description:
Today's no equipment, at home pilates workout is going to be different than all the others because 1) you will be standing the whole time and 2) you WILL NOT let your heels touch the ground!! We'll be doing all the moves on our tippy toes for three minutes straight! This will tone your thighs, your quads, your hamstrings, your calves, and will work the arches of your foot.

Here are your leg slimming exercises:

1. Narrow Squat on tippy toes
2. Lunges on tippy toes
3. Plie Squat on tippy toes
4. Plie Heel Lift

Your calves, thighs & booty should be on fire!!! Which part of your legs felt it the most?

wELrn0f53XI.title: 20 Minute Inner Thigh Isolate Workout | No equipment, at-home Pilates exercises
wELrn0f53XI.description:
Today's workout is specifically focused on isolating the inner thigh muscles. I want you to pay close attention to the placement of my feet, my knees, and my legs if you truly want to get the most effective inner thigh workout possible! Your form and your technique is crucial in this at home, equipment free Pilates thigh workout routine!

In your full length 20 minute workout, we will be doing these 20 inner thigh exercises!

1. Plie squat
2. Heel raise plie right
3. Heel raise plie left
4. Double raise plie
5. Double raise plie pulse
6. Inner thigh flexed pulse right
7. Inner thigh pointed pulse right
8. Inner thigh circles front right
9. Inner thigh circles back right
10. Inner thigh flexed pulse left
11. Inner thigh pointed pulse left
12. Inner thigh circles front left
13. Inner thigh circles back left
14. Sideways scissors
15. Leg circles right, out
16. Leg circles right, in
17. Leg circles left, out
18. Leg circles left, in
19. Butterfly bridge
20. Butterfly bridge pulse

This workout is not easy! But guess what? It's super effective, and super fun to follow along at home. You'll get stronger each time you do it. If you need to take a break, take a quick one, and come right back in. You will get STRONGER and BETTER each time you complete this inner thigh isolation workout. Good luck!

Love, Cassey

ni3w3gNs3AQ.title: 30 Day Ab Challenge Starts Jan 1. You in?
ni3w3gNs3AQ.description:
Get #100abchallenge printable here: https://www.blogilates.com/100abchallenge-begins-jan-1st-you-in/

With the new year coming up, I know a lot of you are looking to change up your workout routines. So, starting Jan. 1st, I want you guys to do the 100 Ab Challenge with me!! We'll be doing 100 reps of a different ab exercise every day for 30 days! And it's all happening here on my YouTube channel - that's one new video EVERY DAY for 30 days! 30 videos!?? OMG. I've never done such a thing!

Is there anyone in particular that you want me to collab with? Comment!!!

HOW IT'S GONNA WORK:

- Take a before pic on Jan. 1 and an after pic on Jan. 30, once you've finished the challenge. At the end, I'll feature some of your transformations!

- Do 100 reps of the ab exercise of the day, on that day! Whether it's 100 reps in 1 round or 10 reps for 10 rounds, doesn't matter. Just get through it!!!

- Use the hashtag #100abchallenge if you decide to post! This will help encourage other POPsters!

- Invite your friends and co workers to do this with you!

- Remember to eat healthy and whole ( you can try the 28 Day Reset on piit28.com ) to make sure your ab muscles will really show through

-Drink lots of water too! Stay hydrated! Plus it keeps you from being bloated.

OKAY! You ready to kill it? COMMENT "I'm in!" if you're ready to commit! Let's go!!!

Here is where I get all of my music! Epidemic Sound: https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

zh2dO7-tgwQ.title: I didn’t eat for 3 days
zh2dO7-tgwQ.description:
I did an experiment and wanted to see what would happen if I didn’t eat any solid food for 3 days. I put myself on a 3 day juice cleanse. Yup. Never thought I’d be saying that.

I decided to try a juice cleanse because my body was in a complete state of chaos after my Hawaii vacation where I ate EVERYTHING my soul desired. Unfortunately, I got so bloated and started breaking out like crazy. My body was NOT happy.

So, here’s a vlog about my entire juice cleanse experience using Pressed Juicery. (NOT SPONSORED)

If you are curious about doing a juice cleanse yourself please do your own research. It would also be good to talk to a nutritionist or your doctor if you are unsure of what your body can handle.

eOWJsw_ARB0.title: 10 Perfect Morning Stretches to Increase Energy
eOWJsw_ARB0.description:
I love the mornings. No phones ringing. No notifications. Total peace.  It's the perfect time to take advantage of the calmness and start your day on a productive note! I always like to wake up and go to the gym, do a PIIT workout, some POP Pilates, or a simple stretch routine!!

Do this 10-move stretch routine before you leave for work or school in the morning to wake up your body for the day! They will open up your chest and shoulders, making you loose and ready to take on whatever comes your way! You’re going to feel SOOOOOO GOOOOOOD!

1. Bent Knee Twist Up
2. Shoulder Stretch Squats
3. Alternating Camel
4. Cat Cow
5. Dancing Dog
6. Plank Walk Opener
7. Plié Twists
8. Yogi Squat
9. Yogi Squat and Straighten
10. Back Bend

Workout starts at 0:59

uQh2dtfNyvo.title: Silent Death Fat Melting Cardio - Apartment Friendly | PIIT28
uQh2dtfNyvo.description:
I wanted to make this apartment-friendly workout for you guys because getting a good workout in without disturbing your neighbors is so hard. I mean, when I lived in an apartment on the FIRST FLOOR, my UPSTAIRS neighbors would always bang on their floor when I worked out. I still don't get it!!!

It's definitely hard to get a solid cardio workout in when you feel like you have to walk on eggshells, but these seven total body toning PIIT moves are are all super quiet fat burning exercises that are easy to do at home!!

Do you have any crazy neighbors? Tell me about them in the comments!!

Remember to go as hard as you can for 45 seconds before your 15 second rest on each move!! I wanna see you guys shake!! Do 4 rounds for a total 28 minute workout.

1. Fast squats
2. Hip twists
3. Alternating front lunge
4. Leg outs
5. Single legged squat & lift
6. Push up ankle tap
7. Plié punches

You can replay this video three more times if you want to get the full workout, or just download the PIIT Pocket app and create the custom workout there!

PIIT Pocket for iPhone: bit.ly/piitpocket
PIIT Pocket for Android: bit.ly/piitpocketandroid

Workout starts at 1:33!

Here is where I get all of my music! Epidemic Sound: https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

localized.title: Silent Death Fat Melting Cardio - Apartment Friendly | PIIT28
localized.description:
I wanted to make this apartment-friendly workout for you guys because getting a good workout in without disturbing your neighbors is so hard. I mean, when I lived in an apartment on the FIRST FLOOR, my UPSTAIRS neighbors would always bang on their floor when I worked out. I still don't get it!!!

It's definitely hard to get a solid cardio workout in when you feel like you have to walk on eggshells, but these seven total body toning PIIT moves are are all super quiet fat burning exercises that are easy to do at home!!

Do you have any crazy neighbors? Tell me about them in the comments!!

Remember to go as hard as you can for 45 seconds before your 15 second rest on each move!! I wanna see you guys shake!! Do 4 rounds for a total 28 minute workout.

1. Fast squats
2. Hip twists
3. Alternating front lunge
4. Leg outs
5. Single legged squat & lift
6. Push up ankle tap
7. Plié punches

2IRneMbgUJo.title: 5 Lower Ab Isolation Exercises That Will Make Your Lower Belly Fat Cry
2IRneMbgUJo.description:
Why does it feel like body fat just goes straight to the lower belly? Like, why can't just a tiny bit go to the booty?? Well, I'm about to drop some knowledge on ya! It's not just what you eat that affects those levels of fat, it's also the amount of sleep you get AND how stressed you are feeling. Lack of sleep and stress can increase your cortisol hormone levels and oddly, that can contribute to an increase in lower belly fat. 

These five lower ab exercises are JUST what you need if you want to attack the lower belly pooch area (plus more sleep and less stress)!! They isolate your lower abdominals to really blast that belly fat! You can do this whole workout ANYWHERE, no weights required!!

1. Crunched heel taps x 1:30
2. Little U's x 1:30
3. Single leg drop x 1:30
4. Heel push abs x 1:30
5. Reverse double leg lift x 1:30

Workout starts at 1:42!

QauFM1Ra4wY.title: Here's how much water you should drink every day...
QauFM1Ra4wY.description:
Join the #30daywaterchallenge! Let’s drink at least half our body weight in fluid ounces everyday from Sept 1-Sept 30! You can grab 
 the 2 printables to track everything here: https://www.blogilates.com/30-day-water-challenge/

For the past few months I have been getting ready for the wedding in every way possible, but now that it's just ONE MONTH away so it's time to focus on my skin!!

Many websites like WebMD say, when it comes to water, we should be drinking at least half our body weight in fluid oz EVERY DAY! Like if you're 140 pounds, you should be drinking 70 oz of water every day. 

So I will be drinking at least 64 oz of water every day for the next 30 days! Wanna do it to? I invite you to join me on the #30daywaterchallenge! Sept 1-Sept 30!

I want YOU to do it with me because you never know how much increasing your water intake will positively affect your body (it's probably a lot)! You’ll feel less bloated, less ravenous, and more energetic! Plus your dry skin will hopefully become a lot more supple! Personally when I drink more water, it clears up my skin!

Make sure to take a before and after picture!

Can't wait to see everyone's results!!

Get your Timer Bottle: https://www.popflexactive.com/collections/water-bottles

Here is where I get all of my music! Epidemic Sound: https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

My outfit & yoga mat are from: http://www.popflexactive.com

wVwNMpYA9cM.title: The one app every active girl needs
wVwNMpYA9cM.description:
My new app PIIT Pocket is FREE to download! ♡ iPhone: http://bit.ly/piitpocket |  ♡ Android: http://bit.ly/piitpocketandroid

PIIT Pocket is like having a personal trainer and a nutritionist with you at all times, motivating and inspiring you to work out and eat healthy!

#1. THERE’S A WORKOUT TIMER WITH MUSIC!

I will demonstrate the move for you on screen while the timer counts down your exercises! You don’t need any equipment or a gym. Plus! You’ll also get to pick your favorite songs from Spotify to play as you sweat!

#2. YOU CAN CREATE YOUR OWN WORKOUTS!

Ever wish you could easily make your own workout routines? Now you can! Just drag and drop moves from the exercise library and make your very own 28 minute dream PIIT routine.

#3. MEAL PLANNING IS EASY!

Featuring over 300+ healthy recipes, you’ll have access to The 28 Day Reset meal plans, including vegan options! But if there’s something you don’t like, no worries, swap out a recipe and create your own meal plan.

#4. BEST COLLECTION OF FREE WORKOUT VIDEOS!

You’ll have direct access to the entire Blogilates workout video library. Choose from categories such as Abs, Back, Butt, Cardio, Legs, Thighs, Obliques, Arms, and Total Body. You can do all the videos from the comfort of your own home. 

#5. A WORKOUT CALENDAR TO KEEP YOU ACCOUNTABLE!

Schedule all your workouts and your meals, and check off as you go. You can even set workout reminders! That means right before your workout, I will motivate you to get your shoes on and and get moving!

Subscription pricing & terms:

PIIT Pocket is free to download with complimentary access to a sample program of PIIT28 1.0, a sample program of The 28 Day Reset and total free access to the Blogilates workout video library. 

For exclusive, updated content, plus full access to all the PIIT28 workout programs and 28 Day Reset meal plans, you’ll want to subscribe to the monthly membership. Not only is it so much cheaper than hiring a personal trainer, it’s way more affordable than a gym membership and you can do all of the workouts from home! Which means, you’re going to be saving a lot of time (and gas) not driving!

hJ7-9CJuMD8.title: 5 Underbutt Isolation Exercises for Ultimate Booty Lift
hJ7-9CJuMD8.description:
The underbutt. The part of your booty that you can grab under. The part where the glute meets the hamstring. The part that sorta shows when your shorts are too short! Haha. You know what I mean?!

Here is an at home, equipment free workout video that you can do to target the exact underbutt area. This means we will be working a lot of hamstrings (biceps femoris, semitendinosis, semimembranosis)  in order to give your booty (your gluteus maximus, minimus, and medius) a lift from underneath.

We will be doing each of the following exercises for 1:30 each, no breaks!

1. Walking Bridge Combo
2. Single Leg Swivel (Right)
3. Single Leg Swivel (Left)
4. Grasshopper
5. Hamstring Curls

Workout starts at 1:51!

Here is where I get all of my music! Epidemic Sound: https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

cCgDB5SMlKE.title: What is Blogilates?
cCgDB5SMlKE.description:
If anyone ever wants to step into the world of Blogilates, tell them to watch this reel! Blogilates is more than just workouts...it's a COMMUNITY of POPsters who live and breathe POP Pilates. We THRIVE on supporting one another towards success. We BELIEVE in working out because it makes you a better, stronger, more positive person...it's more than just vanity. People who do POP Pilates have found the JOY in exercise.

Blogilates is the #1 female fitness channel on YouTube led by certified fitness instructor, entrepreneur, & creator of POP Pilates and best-selling author Cassey Ho. Her format POP Pilates is now the official Pilates of all 24 Hour Fitness gyms nationwide. She's been featured on numerous national publications, in magazines, on shows such as Good Morning America & Dr. Oz and is currently named one of the Top 5 Health & Fitness Influencers in the World by Greatist.

She is also the creator of PIIT28 and her activewear line, POPFLEX.

localized.title: What is Blogilates?
localized.description:
If anyone ever wants to step into the world of Blogilates, tell them to watch this reel! Blogilates is more than just workouts...it's a COMMUNITY of POPsters who live and breathe POP Pilates. We THRIVE on supporting one another towards success. We BELIEVE in working out because it makes you a better, stronger, more positive person...it's more than just vanity. People who do POP Pilates have found the JOY in exercise.

Blogilates is the #1 female fitness channel on YouTube led by certified fitness instructor, entrepreneur, & creator of POP Pilates and best-selling author Cassey Ho. Her format POP Pilates is now the official Pilates of all 24 Hour Fitness gyms nationwide. She's been featured on numerous national publications, in magazines, on shows such as Good Morning America & Dr. Oz and is currently named one of the Top 5 Health & Fitness Influencers in the World by Greatist.

She is also the creator of PIIT28 and her activewear line, POPFLEX.

UClTz7aEIy0.title: 5 things I wish I could tell my 22-year old self | Commencement Speech to the Class of 2018
UClTz7aEIy0.description:
This year I had the INCREDIBLE HONOR of coming back to my Alma Mater, Whittier College and giving the Commencement Speech for the graduating Class of 2018! I really cannot believe it has been 9 years since I've graduated! Here's my speech. Hope it inspires you in some way!

*****

5 Things I Wish I Could Tell my 22-Year Old Self
By: Cassey Ho

Being back here on campus makes me so emotional. I mean, when I look at Stauffer, I can vividly see the moment my mom and dad left me as a little freshman crying my face off like an abandoned child as they drove away.

When I look at the Science Building, I can see myself frantically walking up the stairs in a hoodie and top knot, trying to last minute memorize the 4 nitrogenous bases found in DNA. Guanine, Adenine, Thymine, Cytosine. Right Dr. Bourgaize?

And when I look at the CI, I remember all the food I stuffed myself with because I treated every meal like I was at Hometown Buffet. Let’s just say the Freshman 15 was very real.

Seeing these buildings again and seeing my professors again makes me realize how much Whittier played a role in sculpting me into the person I am today. So many micro-decisions were made right here, that at the time, I thought were trivial. But they ended up changing the entire course of my career.

Graduates, I am really excited to have the honor to speak to you today. From Poet to Poet and peer to peer, I really want to take this opportunity to have a real talk with you before you march across this stage into adulthood. If you’re feeling lost or unsure of what you’re meant to do, don’t worry. That’s normal. Your 20s are meant for figuring these things out. Actually, the rest of your life is meant for figuring things out, but hopefully you will have learned a few things by then.

Look, I’m not going to stand here and pretend that I know everything, because I don’t! But I can tell you 5 things I wish I could have told my 22 year old self. 

#1. Love your parents. But know they’re not always right.

As a child of strict Asian immigrant parents, I also grew up being falsely advertised that there were only 3 career options for me. For my Asian brothers and sisters out there, you know what I’m talking about, right?! 

And if you don’t, let me break it down for you.

Us Asian kids only had the choice of becoming a doctor, lawyer, or engineer. That’s it. Any other option was a disgrace to the family. 

My dad decided he wanted a doctor in the family, so that was my fate. The problem was, I didn’t want to have anything to do with being a doctor. I had been sketching gowns ever since I was 6 - sewing clothes for my Barbies and then designing my friends’ prom dresses. But when I told my dad that I wanted to be a fashion designer, he glared at me and said:

“No. You will do no such thing.”

“Why?” I asked.

“If you become a fashion designer, you will be poor. You will be unsuccessful. So...you know what that means, right?”

“What?”

“It means you will have NO FRIENDS!”

Looking back, I think it was the “no friends” part that really got to me. So I dutifully accepted my fate, tucked my dream away, and went off to major in Biology and minor in Business.

But it wouldn’t be long before I realized how painful it was to be living out someone else’s dream while sacrificing my own.

#2. Take responsibility for your own destiny.

...you can read the rest of my commencement speech at http://www.blogilates.com


******

Cassey Ho is an award-winning fitness instructor, entrepreneur and online personality. As the creator behind Blogilates, the #1 female fitness channel on YouTube, she’s transformed millions of lives through helping them achieve their strength and weight-loss goals. She focuses on making fitness fun and the results are evident. Cassey's unique format, POP Pilates©, which launched as a workout video on YouTube in 2009, has become a live fitness class that can be taken at gyms all over the world with over 3,000 POP Pilates classes being taught monthly. Her authenticity continues to shine through, making her one of the most relatable fitness icons online and beyond. She's also the author of the best-selling book, Hot Body Year Round and is the designer of her own activewear line, POPFLEX.

With a wide range of free workout videos available, Cassey's channel focuses on ab exercises, butt & thigh exercises, arm exercises, pilates, cardio routines, fat burning workouts, high intensity interval training workouts (HIIT), stretching and flexibility routines and so much more!

Z2VCMJJLFEc.title: Came Here for LOVE...HANDLES! Toughest Muffintop Workout EVER!
Z2VCMJJLFEc.description:
When I created this move, I thought okay, no big deal just a couple minutes each side and this muffintop melting song challenge will be over. UMM. WAS I WRONG!!!

I have never suffered this much with any move. This love handles workout to Sigala's "Came Here for Love" nearly killed me. You will work your obliques, your shoulders, your hips, your thighs, your abs - basically your entire total body will be sore!

If you're ready to do this crazy love handles workout, then let's get to it! You can always modify too, just drop the bottom knee. Good luck!

Video starts at 2:00!

Do the 100 Squat Challenge: https://www.blogilates.com/100squatseveryday1/

PEwVYMTHEOg.title: What if we did 100 squats everyday for 30 days?
PEwVYMTHEOg.description:
What would happen if we did 100 squats everyday for 30 days? Well, let's find out! On June 1st, I am going to begin doing 100 squats daily, and I'm gonna do it live on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/blogilates/ at 9AM PST everyday until June 30th. 

If you join in, you'll be entered to win one of FIVE $100 giftcards to POPFLEX! https://www.popflexactive.com/ All you have to do is post a photo on June 30 on IG and talk about what gains you got from the #100squatchallenge experience! You can be from any country, any age. Just make sure your profile is public and you are hashtagging your pic, or else I can't see it! Winners will be chosen randomly!

Everyday we will be doing a new variation of a squat. You can get the entire graphic on my IG @blogilates or always on my blog https://www.blogilates.com/ under Workout ＞ Challenges. Here are all the different types of squats we will be doing:

1. Basic squat
2. Narrow squat
3. Plie squat
4. Releve squat pulse
5. Figure 4 squat
6. Single legged squat
7. Split Squat
8. Single releve plie squat
9. Goblet squat
10. Double releve plie squat
11. Lateral squat
12. Bulgarian Squat
13. Chair squats
14. Jump squats
15. Pretzel squat
16. In n Out Squats
17. Curtsy Squat
18. Basic squat pulses
19. Narrow squat pulses
20. Plie squat pulses
21. Squat Step Backs
22. Split Squat Pulses
23. Single Legged Chair Squats
24. Push Peddler Squat
25. Galloping Wall Squat
26. Side Tap Squat
27. Staggered Squat
28. Squat Lunges
29. Kick back squat
30. Knee Get Up Squat

Good luck! Let's see what these 100 daily squats do to our booty gains and our strength gains!

s0CkBw5Wock.title: *Special* Full Length 1 Hour POP Pilates Class!
s0CkBw5Wock.description:
Wanna become a certified POP Pilates Instructor? Go to http://www.poppilateslife.com to get all the details!

The video you're seeing today is from the official POP Pilates Instructor vault. Normally, these videos are ONLY for people who are certified (they are videos that will help teach an instructor the choreography they need to teach a live group fitness class), but I thought it'd be cool to share a full length class with you here on YouTube. This way, you'll know what to expect when you attend a live POP Pilates class at your local gym!

Each POP Pilates live workout class is about 1 hour long and takes you all the way from the warm up through to the hundreds, ab challenges, butt challenges, arm sculpting combos, thigh toning exercises, core strengthening moves, cardio bursts and then finally we end with flexibility training and stretching.

I hope you enjoy the full length POP Pilates class! I am joined here by 2 of my amazing POP Pilates Instructors Jess and Jaquie!

Follow Jess: https://www.instagram.com/jess_likethat_/
Follow Jaquie: https://www.instagram.com/littlejaquiecan/

We are all wearing outfits from http://www.popflexactive.com

lDs8h7hf9OA.title: Pup Pilates: How to workout at home with your dog!
lDs8h7hf9OA.description:
OMG OMG OMG you guys we are doing PUP Pilates with my very first, very own PUPPY!!!! AHHHHHHHH!!!!!!! This is Sir George The Magnificent! https://www.instagram.com/sirgeorgethemagnificent/ He is the fluffy love of my life! He's a Pomapoo and currently weighs in at about 4 lbs! I cannot believe that I actually have a dog now. I've spent way too many years as #CasseytheDogStalker. Finally, finally, I have a puppy to do PUP Pilates with! I AM SO HAPPY. YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND!

Whenever I try to work out at home with Sir George, he just ends up biting all my fingers and toes, licks my entire face, and pulls on my hair. So, I legit cannot work out with him in the room. So...this prompted me to see what I could do if I worked out with him in my arms! 

Today I want you to grab your pet - if you don't have one, a weight or some object will do - and do these exercises with me! Have fun! Let's do some DOGILATES!

0QoV3XetmUg.title: 6 Natural Pre-Workout + Post-Workout Snacks Ideas!
0QoV3XetmUg.description:
Do you ever wonder if you need to be having a pre workout or post workout snack? Is it necessary to eat before and after you exercise to keep those gainz in check!? Well, the truth is - it depends on your body! In this video, we're going to talk about what types of food you should be eating before and after your workout to fuel you up!

Thanks to Sunkist for sponsoring this video! 

To learn more about the health benefits of citrus and to check out more really tasty citrus recipes, check out: https://bit.ly/2EJt9Ii

PRE-WORKOUT SNACKS:

Here are 3 all natural pre-workout snacks that you can eat to give you energy! They are all carb-ilicious!

#1. Tropical Energy Smoothie

- 1 Sunkist Navel Orange
- 1 Banana
- 1/3 C frozen pineapples

#2. DIY Sports Drink

- 1/2 C water
- 1 C Coconut Water
- 1 Sunkist Lemon
- 1 TBS honey
- 1 pinch salt

or keep it simple and just keep it simple and eat...

#3. A whole fruit! For example, a banana, an apple, an orange, a grapefruit, a nectarine, some berries. Whateve fruit you like!

POST-WORKOUT SNACKS:

When choosing a post workout snack, pick something with a good mix of protein and carbs. The protein will help rebuild your muscles. The carbs will help replenish your energy stores.

#1. Protein shake with a banana

#2. String cheese, almonds, and an orange

#3. Hummus and Veggies

l0Lfg4szAjM.title: Backless Bride Back Toning Workout | BRIDAL BOOTCAMP
l0Lfg4szAjM.description:
I love love LOVE backless dresses. So gonna let you in on a little secret...my wedding dress is actually going to backless! But that is all I will tell you! But because of this, I made sure to make us the BEST backless dress workout that was ever created!

The great thing about working your back is that it will improve your posture, make you look taller, and also look more confident! It's a win for you big time. Lucky for you, there is no equipment, you don't need a gym, and you can do this workout anywhere! But especially at home :) Have fun!

Every workout in the Blogilates Bridal Bootcamp is 10 minutes long with NO BREAKS. There are 10 moves that are done for 1 minute each, back to back. I'm training you this way to save you time while teaching your muscles to get stronger with intense moves in a very short amount of time. 

The 10 cardio exercises for your Bridal Bootcamp are:

1. Walnut Crushers
2. Goal Post Puncher
3. Reverse Plank Lifts
4. Bird Dog Pulses R
5. Bird Dog Pulses L
6. Parachuters
7. Half Cobra Grasshopper
8. Snow Angel Belly
9. Flying Bird Dog R
10. Flying Bird Dog L

If you are starting to do some of your own wedding planning, I recommend you check out http://www.TheKnot.com. You can create your own wedding website for free as well as search for great vendors in your area.

Y2did1lMbd4.description:
Welcome to the Blogilates Bridal Bootcamp! Your first video in this series focuses on your upper abs, lower abs, obliques and your waist. Why? When we work on your core, it not only helps tighten and strengthen your midsection, but it also helps you stand taller which makes you appear more confident! And don't you want to look and feel confident as you walk down the aisle? YES!

HJ_Zj8N0cSc.title: Can DNA ACTUALLY influence how much you weigh?
HJ_Zj8N0cSc.description:
Find out what your genes have to say about your weight! New Year’s Promotion! Go to http://23andMe.com/blogilates to save $30 on a Health + Ancestry kit, now through January 31st.

I did the 23andme genetic testing service and OMG guys, it explains so much about my weight. Growing up I ALWAYS had trouble losing weight. I was the chubby kid. I was the fat one. When it came to working out and dieting, I had to train so hard and eat so clean to only see results that don't even compare the girls who can eat junk food all day and still have flat abs. So it always made me wonder, am I just supposed to be "fat"? Am I predestined to have a soft body with no ab definition? Is it in my genes - my DNA - to weigh more?

Watch this video to find out what my DNA says about my weight. You'll find the information shocking. It pretty much explains why there is no such thing as a diet or a workout that works for everyone. We are all so different. 

Here is where I get all of my music! Epidemic Sound: https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

bHD3Su6PaHU.description:

Here are 6 tricks I use to motivate myself to work out! Thanks to Samsung for sponsoring this video!

3. I keep a gym bag in my car with shoes, socks, clothes, headphones, and a towel so I'm always prepared to work out! No excuses!

rTPaGdSlOv8.title: Your 2018 Reset Challenge is...
rTPaGdSlOv8.description:
Are you ready to take on a challenge that will give you the momentum you need to make a lasting change in your body and your mindset...for the rest of your life?

Good, because I am too. 2017 was a rough year for me personally and professionally, so that ended up affecting how I ate and how much time I had to exercise. It didn't feel good. And I don't want to enter the new year feeling this way anymore. So if you're up for it, I challenge you to take the 2018 Reset Challenge with me. You in?!

The 2018 Reset Challenge rules:

1. Challenge begins Jan 1, 2018. Take a before picture (front/side/back) in a bikini or in sports bra and shorts.

2. PART 1 - THE FOOD: You will only eat Reset-friendly foods.

3. PART 2 - THE WORKOUT: You will be active for 30 minutes a day, 6x a week.

4. Challenge ends Jan 28, 2018. Take an after picture (front/side/back) all from the same angle and in the same outfit as your before picture. Share your results with hashtag #28dayreset!

FREE 28 DAY RESET PDF: http://www.blogilates.com/blog/2017/12/26/your-2018-reset-challenge-is/
PERFECT 10 COOKBOOK: https://www.piit28.com/store/rL9wMXto

The challenge is only 28 days long, but will set you up for a lifetime of understanding your body. Having acne, feeling bloated, being tired, and carrying around extra "stubborn" fat doesn't feel good, and you deserve nothing less than feeling amazing. The truth is, we've gotten used to thinking the above is "normal". But it doesn't have to be your normal. Your normal should be your best. 

Good luck guys! Let's show 2018 who's BOSS!!!!

Here is where I get all of my music! Epidemic Sound: https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

qyaMZiChWM0.title: KICK BUTT BLASTER | PIIT28 Street Fighter Inspired Workout
qyaMZiChWM0.description:
Ready to get your butt and thighs WORKING?!? Our superhero themed PIIT28 workout series continues with inspiration from one of the toughest (and strongest!) characters ever, Chun-Li from Street Fighter! Today we’re burning fat with this total body workout and kicking away the negativity! Hiyahhh!

Your moves:

1. Shuffle bounce

2. Plié calf raise

3. Front kicks

4. Plié punches

5. Squat side kick right

6. Lunge kicks

7. Squat side kick left

Perform each move for 45 seconds. Rest 15 seconds in between. Repeat the entire series of moves 4 times through for a 28 minute long workout. If you want the entire PIIT28 experience, go to https://piit28.com!

nYwhZwA9JZo.title: 5 Easy & Creative Avocado Recipes | CHEAP CLEAN EATS
nYwhZwA9JZo.description:
Today we get to cook with my fave...AVOCADOS!! Um, my mouth is already watering. Avocados are high in healthy fats and great for keeping you fuller longer! All the recipes today are SUPER simple to make and BONUS, they are 100% Vegan. Be sure to post any photos of your masterpieces with #cheapcleaneats so I can see what you make! Get creative! All of these recipes have wiggle room too!

#1 Avo Hummus Toast

INGREDIENTS:
1/4 Avocado
1 Ezekiel bread slice
1 TBSP Beet humus
1 slice Heirloom tomato
Pinch of Salt
Pinch of Pepper

DIRECTIONS:
Cut 1/4 of the avocado into small slices.
Toast your ezekiel bread.
Lather your toast with beet humus.
Slice up the heirloom tomato.
Add the avocado and tomato to your toast.
Add a pinch of salt and pepper

#2 Avocado Salsa

INGREDIENTS:
Small handful Cilantro
1 large tomato
1 Avocado
1 cup Roasted Corn
1 Lime
Pinch of Pepper
Tapatio to taste
Bag of Plantain chips

DIRECTIONS:
Chop up a handful of cilantro.
Cut the large tomato into slices.
Chop up one avocado.
Add the cilantro, tomato, and avocado into a bowl.
Add roasted corn to the bowl.
Season with lime juice.
Add in a few drops of Tapatio hot sauce.
Sprinkle some pepper.

#3. Happy Vegan Sandwich

INGREDIENTS:
A few slices of Red Onion
A few slices of Cucumber
A few thick slices of Avocado (Umm and yes I forgot to add them in the video OOPS)
1 thick slice of Heirloom Tomato
2 Ezekiel toast slices
2 TBSP Hummus
2 Butter lettuce leaves
Small bunch of Alfafa sprouts

DIRECTIONS:
Chop up 1/4 of a red onion.
Chop up 1/4 of a cucumber.
Slice 1/2 an avocado.
Slice your heirloom tomato.
Toast 2 pieces of ezekiel toast.
Add 2 tbsp of hummus to toast.
Add 2 pieces of butter lettuce.
Add a small bunch of alfalfa sprouts.
Layer the red onion, cucumber, and tomato on the toast.

#4. Avocado Fries

INGREDIENTS:
5 avocados
2 cups Non dairy milk
1 cup Garbanzo Flour
1 TBSP Garlic Powder
Salt and pepper
2 cups Coconut Flakes
Coconut Oil

Dipping sauce:
Small handful of Cilantro
4 TBSP Vegan mayo
Chipotle tabasco sauce to taste
Squeeze of lime to taste

DIRECTIONS:
Cut up 5 avocados in a chunky fashion.
Fill up a bowl with 2 cups of non dairy milk.
In a separate bowl, pour one cup of garbanzo flour.
Add 1 tbsp of garlic powder to garbanzo flour.
Add a pinch of salt and pepper.
Pour two cups of coconut flakes onto a plate.
Dip pieces of avocado into each batter and then cover in coconut flakes.
Spray coconut oil over everything.
Bake for 15-18 minutes at 420 degrees F.

Dipping sauce:
Chop up cilantro.
Add 4 tbsp of vegan mayo.
Add 1 tbsp Chipotle Tabasco sauce.
Add a squeeze of lime.

#5. “Fried” Avo Tacos

INGREDIENTS:
1/8 of a Red cabbage, sliced
1 corn tortilla
2 Avocado fries
1 TBSP Avocado fries sauce

DIRECTIONS:
Chop up 1/8 of red cabbage into small slivers.
Place it on corn tortilla.
Add in the avocado fries.
Top it with cilantro and a squeeze of lime.
Drizzle sauce from Avocado fries.

Happy eating!!

qodPTshCVd4.title: How to Make Unicorn Toast (Vegan) | CHEAP CLEAN EATS
qodPTshCVd4.description:
I'm bored with toast. It needs more color. So today let's make UNICORN toast. Huh??!! What?!? YEAH imagine rainbow toast because you know I love me some rainbows! This colorful and fun food trend is taking over Instagram, so I wanted to put a healthy spin on it for all of you. I’m going to show you how to make a VEGAN version of Unicorn Toast using plant based cream cheese and all natural colorings! Absolutely nothing artificial in our Unicorn Toast. 

Ingredients I used:

Ezekiel bread
Vegan cream cheese
Beet juice for natural pink dye
Frozen blueberries for natural purple dye
Turmeric for natural yellow dye
Matcha for natural green eye

Extra toppings:

Bananas
Blueberries
Raspberries

If you make the Unicorn Toast, please hashtag #cheapcleaneats and tag @blogilates so I can see it! It would make my day to see you cooking and having fun!

fd2zFJ3QRzk.title: When Disney Princesses Go on a Diet...
fd2zFJ3QRzk.description:
Have you ever wondered what Disney princesses had to eat (or not eat) to look so good? Were they all on diets or something? Would Pocahontas be vegan? Would Belle and Beast be carnivores? Would Elsa want everything to be raw and frozen? Well, today Elsa, Belle, Ariel, Jasmine, Aurora, and Pocahontas are getting together to have a picnic...and...umm...let's just say things get a little out of hand as their diets clash to the max.

THE CAST

Madilyn Bailey as Elsa from "Frozen"
Lindsey Stirling as Ariel from "The Little Mermaid"
Lilly Singh aka iiSuperwomanii as "Jasmine from Aladdin"
Rosanna Pansino as Belle from "Beauty and the Beast"
Justine Ezarik aka iJustine as Aurora from "Sleeping Beauty"
Cassey aka Blogilates as Pocahontas from "Pocahontas"


Make sure you guys subscribe to all my friends! They are so incredible! I'm so glad we were able to get together again to do this in between all of our crazy schedules. Plus I loved being able to introduce a new princess to the mix! Maddy is PERFECT for Elsa right!?

Madilyn: https://www.youtube.com/user/MadilynBailey
Lindsey: https://www.youtube.com/user/lindseystomp
Lilly: https://www.youtube.com/user/IISuperwomanII
Ro: https://www.youtube.com/user/RosannaPansino
Justine: https://www.youtube.com/user/ijustine

******

Cassey Ho is an award-winning fitness instructor, entrepreneur and online personality. As the creator behind Blogilates, the #1 female fitness channel on YouTube, she’s transformed millions of lives through helping them achieve their strength and weight-loss goals. She focuses on making fitness fun and the results are evident. Cassey's unique format, POP Pilates©, which launched as a workout video on YouTube in 2009, has become a live fitness class that can be taken at gyms all over the world with over 3,000 POP Pilates classes being taught monthly. Her authenticity continues to shine through, making her one of the most relatable fitness icons online and beyond. She's also the author of the best-selling book, Hot Body Year Round and is the designer of her own activewear line, POPFLEX.

With a wide range of free workout videos available, Cassey's channel focuses on ab exercises, butt & thigh exercises, arm exercises, pilates, cardio routines, fat burning workouts, high intensity interval training workouts (HIIT), stretching and flexibility routines and so much more!

***

uyBySoB6hNs.title: 5 Moves to Lift Your Butt & 5 Tips for Living your Best Life
uyBySoB6hNs.description:
I am loving the calm feel of this vloggy type exercise series. What do you guys think? Do you like it? Today we are going to be working your glutes - giving you a great kick butt booty routine as I discuss my life tips for living the life that you want. If you take just one of these tips and apply it to your life now, you will see a positive change that will set you on the path to your own personal success. 

5 butt lifting exercises:

1. Straight leg pulses
2. Straight leg circles
3. Low rainbow butt
4. Cross butt kick
5. Side pulse of death

5 life tips for living up to your potential:

1. Do more of what makes you happy. Do less of what doesn't.
2. Just do it.
3. Don't live your life for other people.
4. Don't expect things.
5. Delete negative people out of your life.

JZyy0JfUNXQ.title: 5 Ways to Build your Core & Confidence Workout
JZyy0JfUNXQ.description:
Did you know that regular exercise can improve your memory and learning skills? That's why I'm taking it up a notch by having you learn WHILE you exercise!!! So in this next series of videos, I'll be sharing life tips, life hacks, my personal experiences and stories to help you guys build confidence, make new friends, take chances, kill it in your careers, and follow your dreams. 

After all...I know some of you guys watch my videos without doing them...so it'll almost be like a vlog where I am moving around the entire time!

Your 5 ab flattening, core strengthening moves are:

1. Infinity Abs
2. Boat Crunch
3. Twisted Crunch
4. Single Leg Drop
5. Single Leg Situp

Your 5 confidence building tips are:

1. Find what you are good at!
2. Kill negative thoughts
3. Give compliments
4. Prepare
5. Keep Learning

oykL0mDi2qo.title: 5 Scary Things That Happen When You Don't Sleep!
oykL0mDi2qo.description:
There are 3 pillars to being truly healthy. Most people know the 1st two but forget the 3rd:

1. Eating nutritiously 
2. Exercising daily 
3. Sleeping enough 
 
Sleep is everything guys! Don't get enough rest and your body won't function at its best! It makes it hard to lose weight or even learn new things!
 
Guys I'm so excited to be partnering with ZzzQuil to share tips with you on how to get great sleep!
 
I sometimes take ZzzQuil when I'm super jet lagged. I fall asleep in as little as 20 min. It helps me adjust to the new time zone so that I can get my 7-8 hours of sleep and wake up the next day refreshed...and not late to my first event. That's my lil secret!

O3Vf-Tr0NrQ.title: ARMS FOCUS // 6-Week Body Toning Bootcamp #5
O3Vf-Tr0NrQ.description:
Want toned triceps, sculpted shoulders, and amazing arms for tank top season? This workout pairs fat burning cardio with weightless arm exercises for the most effective upper body routine! No dumbbells or equipment needed!

All music from Epidemic Sound (free 30 day trial): https://goo.gl/Nj4ZMg

You will do each exercise 45 sec through with 15 sec of rest in between. For a full 28 minute workout, you must repeat this sequence 4x through...PIIT style!

Your 7 moves are:

1. Mountain Climbers
2. Gecko
3. Tricep Kick n Dip Right
4. Hip Twist Plank Jack
5. Tricep Kick n Dip Left
6. Shoulder Push-Up
7. Triple Tricep Push-Up

The 6-Week challenge is to do the workout of the week (28 min) at least once that week. Do that for 6 consecutive weeks and you will be so much more than bikini body ready...you're gonna be life body ready! 

My outfit & yoga mat are from: http://www.popflexactive.com

-4il6fzEhgM.title: 3 Sweet & Savory Breakfast Ideas: Pancakes, Pudding & Eggs Benedict! 28 Day Reset friendly!
-4il6fzEhgM.description:
If you wanna set a strong and successful tone for the day, start your morning off with some delish breakfast! I know a lot of us don't have time, so I made sure to show you breakfast ideas that are not only nutritious but also super quick and easy to make. Oh yes and they are all 28 Day Reset approved! http://the28dayreset.com/ 

You ready!!?? Let's cook!!!

#1. Healthy Eggs Benedict

Ingredients:

- 1 tbsp nutritional yeast
- 1 tbsp garlic seasoning 
- sea salt & pepper
- 2 1/2 inch slices polenta
- 2 slices Canadian bacon
- 2 eggs
- 2 slices avocado

#2. Simple Apple Pancakes

Ingredients:

- 1/2 small apple
- 2 eggs
- 2 tbsp almond flour
- 2 tbsp coconut flour
- 1/2 tsp baking powder
- 3 tbsp unsweetened apple sauce
- 1tsp nut butter

#3. Cherry Almond Pudding

Ingredients:

- 2/3 c non-dairy milk
- 2/3 c frozen cherries
- 1/4 c rolled oats
- 2 tbsp chia seeds
- Stevia
- 1 tbsp silvered almonds

UBZGjtsB99Y.title: 3 Healthy Lunch Ideas! 28 Day Reset Approved w/ Vegan Options
UBZGjtsB99Y.description:
Today I am sharing with you 3 easy-to-make lunches that you can prepare the night before so you can take them to work or school! They are healthy, yummy and give you that mid-day energy boost you need. They are all 28 Day Reset approved with vegan options, which I know you guys asked for on the last video. Yay I can't wait for you to try them!

#1. BLT Sandwiches

Ingredients:

1 sweet potato
mustard
3-4 slices of bacon
lettuce leaves

Directions.

1. Skin and slice sweet potato into thick sandwich pieces.
2. Bake with coconut oil for 10 min at 400 degrees F.
3. Top with mustard, bacon, lettuce leaves, and tomatoes.

#2. Vegan Tacos

Ingredients:

1 avocado
1/3 c salsa
2tbsp lime juice
3 c shredded cabbage
1 can garbanzo beans
1 beet
2 green onions
salt & pepper
2tbsp fiesta seasoning
8 corn tortillas
pumpkin seeds

Directions:

1. Mash avocado, salsa and lime juice.
2. Add in cabbage, beans, spiralized beets, onions, salt & pepper, fiesta seasoning.
3. Top tortillas with mixture.

#3. Collard Green Burritos

Ingredients:

1/2 c quinoa
1/4 c canned corn
1/4 c salsa
2/3 c refried beans
collard greens
cilantro

Directions:

1. Mix quinoa, corn, salsa and refried beans. Microwave for 30 seconds.
2. Top collard greens with mixture and wrap it up into baby burritos.
3. Cut in half and top with hot sauce if you wish!

sPrcm99Re8A.description:
This is the ultimate upper body workout that will hit your biceps, triceps, shoulders and back. You don't need any equipment and guess what?! There are ZERO pushups. But don't be fooled because you will still get a crazy good workout! You can sit or stand the entire time. But really focus on control and contacting the muscles you are working. You will surprise them with what a great upper body workout you can get with no weights!

Here are the moves:
1. Arm Circles Forward
2. Arm Circles Backwards
3. Peek-A-Boos
4. Back Behinds
5. Reach Ups

j0rgbfeRFVA.title: Lift Your Booty Workout | 5 Moves to Your Fittest Butt
j0rgbfeRFVA.description:
Booty booty booty rocking everywhere! Are you ready for this glute workout that will tone and tighten your booty from every angle!? We will also hit your hamstrings at the same time. There are lots of reps, and little-to-no rest between each exercise, but that is when you need to fight the burn and keep going. We do 5 exercises on the same leg, then switch to the other. Get ready cause it's going to be crazy! Results happen when you push your body and your mind to its limits. Let's GO!

The moves are:
1. Knee Tap Pushes
2. Push Pulses
3. Straight Leg Butt Lift
4. Hammy Curl
5. Pointed Butt Lift

nlFEAKGO79k.title: The Secret Journey of POPFLEX
nlFEAKGO79k.description:
Have you ever wondered how the clothes you wear get made? From fashion illustration to pattern making to sample making to tech packs to fittings and photoshoots...fashion design is an intense PROCESS that takes a team of dedicated people from all over the world. I wanted to create this video to share with you what goes on behind the scenes of my brand new activewear fashion company POPFLEX http://www.popflexactive.com. I really hope you like this and begin to see the creations around you as true artwork and treat your clothes with more gratitude, respect, and appreciation. 

Thank you to the Blogifam for your hard work! 

Wonderful people in the video - listed in order they were featured:

Cassey Ho
Grace Sanchez
Lexi Rivera
Leslie McMullin
Sam Livits
Tiffany Lee
Kassia Phoy
Gracie Dzienny
Taylor Shanle
Daniel DeArco
Sara Litvak

Thank you to the hard working team at LR Creative for helping me bring this video to life! http://www.lrcreativecamp.com/

And for anyone wondering, POPFLEX Activewear is manufactured at a WRAP certified factory with fair wages and fair labor. We create the highest quality activewear for the best price in the market, because we can. We now carry up to plus size 16!

KLFhtWuSv8k.description:
Guys. I just made a Pumpkin Spice Latte that is a bajillion times healthier than the Starbucks version PLUS it's easy, vegan, and so much cheaper! Go make this for you and your family now!

Ingredients:

1 3/4 cup unsweetened vanilla cashew milk
3 tablespoons canned pumpkin
1/4 teaspoon pumpkin pie spice
1/4 teaspoon ground cloves
1 teaspoon maple extract
2 tablespoons maple syrup, and/or stevia to taste
1 chai teabag (herbal)
2 tablespoons CoCoWhip

FcdvsetEYb8.title: 3 Quick & Easy Post Workout Snack Ideas!
FcdvsetEYb8.description:
What makes the perfect post workout meal? One that will help rebuild your muscles, give you energy, and keep you full! That means a combo of BOTH protein, carbs, and a tiny bit of fat. Make sure to eat within 30 to 1 hr post workout for maximal benefits!

#1. BAKED APPLE SUPREME

Ingredients:
1 large apple
2 teaspoons granulated sweetener, honey or maple syrup
1/2 teaspoon cinnamon
3/4 cup vanilla Greek yogurt (or yogurt of choice)
1 tablespoon chopped walnuts or pecans (optional)

Method:
1. Peel the apple (this is optional) and dice or slice thin.
2. Place apples in a bowl, mug or Mason jar and sprinkle with sweetener and cinnamon. 
3. Cover with plastic wrap and microwave for 2 minutes. Carefully remove wrap, top with yogurt, and serve.

Nutrition Info:
Calories: 274 | Protein: 18g | Fat: 5g | Net Carbs: 37g | Fiber: 6g

#2. VEGAN CRUNCH CAKES

Ingredients: 

2 rice cakes 
2 tablespoons almond butter 
1⁄2 cup raspberries (or sliced strawberries)

Method:

1. Spread one tablespoon almond butter on each rice cake. 
2. Top with berries, and serve.

Nutrition Info:

Calories: 292 | Protein: 9g | Fat: 19g | Net Carbs: 20g | Fiber: 8g

#3. BANANA CHEESECAKE PUDDING

Ingredients:

1/2 cup low-fat cottage cheese

1/2 ripe medium banana

2 tablespoons granola

1 teaspoon honey (or stevia to taste)

Method:

1. Add the cottage cheese and banana to a small food processor or mini blender.
2. Process until smooth. Top with granola and sweetener.
3. If desired, stir sweetener into the purée with granola and freeze overnight in popsicle molds for a true “grab and go” post-workout meal.

Nutrition Info:

Calories: 221 | Protein: 14g | Fat: 5g | Net Carbs: 33g | Fiber: 4g

iXuuDY4FswE.title: Healthiest Cake in the World!
iXuuDY4FswE.description:
GUYS. I tried making a cake without using any flour and without baking. It's 100% vegan, fruit based and is the EASIEST and HEALTHIEST cake in the world to make!!! 

Watermelon Cake

Ingredients:
1 medium-large watermelon
1 container coco-whip frozen topping, slightly thawed
1/2 cup sliced almonds
1/4 - 1/3 cup blueberries
1/2 cup sliced strawberries
1-2 kiwi, peeled and sliced
(any other fruit you wish to decorate with)

Method:
1. Slice off 2-inches off each end of the watermelon and discard. 
2. Stand watermelon upright on a flat end on a cutting board. Starting at top of melon, use a long sharp knife to carefully cut between rind and flesh, all around the watermelon. Discard rind.
3. Pat very dry with paper towels. 
4. Frost with coco-whip and decorate in a beautiful design.

Nutrition Info:

Approx calories, depending on the size of watermelon and amount of whip used:

Calories: 183
Protein: 2g                
Fat: 7g
Net Carbs: 28g
Fiber: 2g

7QywGLuayQI.title: Sexy Blueberry Vanilla Milkshake Recipe (Non-Dairy)
7QywGLuayQI.description:
MY MILKSHAKE BRINGS ALL THE BOYS TO THE YARD because THIS is the sexiest milkshake I've ever made in my life. It must be the blueberry jam layer on the bottom or maybe it's the milk jar, but I can't even. You can totally veganize this by omitting the honey. Ready? Let's make this. 

BLUEBERRY VANILLA LAVENDER MILKSHAKE

Yield: 2 servings
Serving Size: 1/2 shake
Prep Time: 1 min

Ingredients:
Blueberry Sauce
1/4 cup low sugar blueberry preserves, stirred well

Shake:
1/4 cup raw cashews, soaked for 2 hours and drained
1 3/4 cups unsweetened vanilla cashew milk
1 frozen banana
1 1/2 cups ice
1 1/2 teaspoons vanilla extract, or vanilla paste
2 teaspoons honey, and/or stevia to taste 
1/2 teaspoon dried lavender
pinch sea salt

Nutrition Info:
Calories: 250
Protein: 3.5g
Fat: 8g
Net Carbs: 58g
Fiber: 2g

OnT_baDv26o.title: Creative, Healthy Lunch Ideas for School & Work!
OnT_baDv26o.description:
If you're spending way too much $ buying lunch everyday, then you need to make a little time to make your own DIY lunches for work or for school. They're quick, they're easy, they're affordable, and they're HEALTHY! Here are 3 back to school, back to work lunch recipes that you can try:

1) Chilled Spinach Avocado Soup

Ingredients:
3 tablespoons raw cashews, soaked 6 hours and drained
2 big handfuls spinach
3/4 cup vegetable broth
1 Persian cucumber, sliced
1 celery stalk, sliced
1/4 cup avocado
2 whole green onions, sliced
1/4 cup basil leaves (optional)
2 tablespoons nutritional yeast
1/4 teaspoon garlic powder
1/4 teaspoon sea salt
Pinch of pepper
1/2 tomato, chopped

2) Salad in a Jar

Ingredients:
2-3 tablespoons light salad dressing
1/3 cup garbanzo beans, drained and rinsed
2 ounces high quality deli turkey, chopped
1/4 cup shredded carrot
1 1/2 cups Romaine lettuce, torn
1/2 cup red bell peppers, chopped
1 ounce crumbled feta cheese
1/2 cup chopped cucumber
4 kalamata olives, sliced


3) Avocado Egg Salad Pita (2 servings)

Ingredients:
1 medium avocado, pitted and peeled
1 teaspoon lemon juice
3 hard-boiled eggs, peeled and chopped
2 hard-boiled egg whites, chopped
1 tablespoon Dijon mustard
1 celery stalk, finely chopped 
1 green onion, chopped
Salt and black pepper, to taste
1 pita bread, cut in half
